    HiveConf

    public static enum HiveConf.ConfVars
extends Enum<HiveConf.ConfVars>
    ConfVars. These are the default configuration properties for Hive. Each HiveConf object is initialized as follows: 1) Hadoop configuration properties are applied. 2) ConfVar properties with non-null values are overlayed. 3) hive-site.xml properties are overlayed. WARNING: think twice before adding any Hadoop configuration properties with non-null values to this list as they will override any values defined in the underlying Hadoop configuration.
